title: ALNA
description: Health store that stocks numerous types of vegan cheese (Cheezly, Soyana, Wilmersburger brands), vegan cream cheese, vegan meats, sausages, hummus and other spreads, grains, cereals, beans, vegan pates, coconut milk, tofu sandwiches, bread, organic fruits, nuts, seeds, spirulina, cruelty free cosmetics, vegan ready made meals such as "gyros," some gluten-free, and other products. The staff is helpful. At the Coutance tram stop of the nr. 14 tram, opposite Manor.
